summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3269 for the improvement of 5th Avenue Northeast, from East 50th Street to the existing concrete sidewalks between East 54th Street and East 55th Street, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 40616, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
